These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball, climbing, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | photography  | hiking | filmmaking | video-games  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | climbing   | skiing  | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, apricot, cauliflower, broccoli
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, librarian, electrician, videographer
1. the videographer is not to the left of the videographer##8
2. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
3. the person eating cucumber is the librarian##1
4. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating apricot##2
5. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the mechanic##7
6. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
7. the mechanic is not to the left of the mechanic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | cauliflower | apricot          | broccoli | cucumber     |
| Job    | electrician      | videographer | mechanic | librarian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, analyst, mechanic, police-officer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, spy, animation
1. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the mechanic##8
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
3. the analyst is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the analyst is in an even position##4
5. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
7. the police-officer is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | engineer | analyst | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | animation   | documentary | spy    |

