.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, indie, pop, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, tennis, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
5. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the fan of pop is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | indie         | gospel   | punk    |
| Sport         | cricket | biathlon | tennis | skiing |

