.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, sports, animation
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, golf, skateboarding, baseball
1. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
2. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
3. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
4. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's sport is golf##7
6. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
7. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
8. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | sports | animation | documentary    |
| Sport         | rowing | baseball   | skateboarding   | golf |

