.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pear, tomato, apricot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, salsa, rock, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
3. the person eating tomato is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person eating pear##5
6. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
7. the person eating apricot is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | grapes | pear  | tomato |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | r&b         | rock | reggae |

