.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, soccer, cycling
1. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is soccer##7
3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
5. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | lemonade | hot-chocolate | coffee   |
| Sport      | baseball | soccer | cycling  | swimming |

