.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, r&b, ambient, disco
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, car, skateboard, quad-bike
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of disco and the person driving the train##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
5. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
6. the fan of ambient is not the person driving the skateboard##6
7. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
8. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | punk | ambient | r&b |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car       | train  | skateboard    |

