2. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
4. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the american##8
5. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the canadian##8
6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
