.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, carrot, spinach, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, chess, card-games, magic-tricks
1. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person eating carrot##8
3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating spinach is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
7. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | carrot        | grapefruit | spinach      | kale    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | card-games   | chess | magic-tricks |

