.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, coffee, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, sailing, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person drinking lemonade##7
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water | lemonade         | coffee    | sprite       |
| Sport      | sailing | swimming | surfing | volleyball |

