.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, pomegranate, broccoli, spinach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, thriller, spy, romance
 1. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 2. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
 3. the person eating raspberry is the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
 7. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 9. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
10. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | pomegranate    | broccoli | raspberry | spinach |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance  | spy     | thriller    |

