.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, orange, peach, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, sudoku, magic-tricks, card-games
1. the person eating peach is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating orange##1
6. the person eating orange is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating zucchini##2
7. the person eating peach is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
