.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, ferret, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, train, snowmobile
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person driving the train##6
2. the person driving the train is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
7. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | guinea-pig | goldfish  | ferret  |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter   | snowmobile | train |

