.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, mouse, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the ship is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
4. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the train##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the train##7
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the quad-bike and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | cat    | guinea-pig | snake | mouse |
| Transport   | ship | quad-bike      | boat     | train     |

 